<P>
Three University of Cincinnati basketball players who violated NCAA rules by 
receiving financial aid have paid the money back, according to Rick Taylor, 
University of Cincinnati athletic director. 
</P>
<P>
The players, Louis Banks, Keith Starks and Levertis Robinson, all are seniors 
at Cincinnati. The violations occurred during their freshman seasons. 
</P>
