<P>
ON THE RECORD 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
"And always remember, the weak, meek and ignorant are always good targets." 
</P>
<P>
 -- Tip sheet given to salespersons at Lincoln S&amp;L. 
</P>
</TEXT>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA091990-0093 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 278392 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
September 19, 1990, Wednesday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
