<HEADLINE>
<P>
PHILHARMONIC SOCIETY RECEIVES TWO GRANTS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By ZAN DUBIN 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
The Orange County Philharmonic Society has received two grants for education 
and community outreach programs. 
</P>
<P>
The Times Orange County Edition has contributed $25,000 plus services to help 
support the society's "Cruise of Lights," an annual series of holiday boat 
cruises of decorated homes and waterways in Huntington Harbour, scheduled Dec. 
13 through 21. 
</P>
<P>
Toshiba America, which will not disclose the amount of its gift, will help 
underwrite the society's fifth-grade youth concerts. ZAN DUBIN 
</P>
</TEXT>
<SUBJECT>
<P>
GRANTS; ORANGE COUNTY PHILHARMONIC SOCIETY 
